lead_paragraph: France included RC Toulon's Charles Ollivon in a 32-man squad on Wednesday to prepare for the November tests despite the player not featuring on coach Guy Noves's initial elite list.

headline.print_headline: Ollivon Gets France Call-Up for November Tests
